tests/__fixtures__/tmp/
.pr-body.md

# Misplaced cross-drive paths (Windows: when a tool drops "E:/..."
# inside this repo, the colon gets encoded to U+F03A by Win32; treat
# any literal "E:/" or its encoded form as junk that must never ship.
# The literal-codepoint rule lives at the bottom of this file because
# git is byte-strict and the U+F03A char is invisible in most editors).
E:/

# ── Local experimental scripts (per-user, may contain PII) ──────────────────
# These belong to individual user sessions / forks. The canonical features
# they prototype eventually land in tracked scripts (auto-apply.mjs, scan.mjs,
# etc.). Until then, keep them local.
apply-one.mjs
assemble-package.mjs
auto-pipeline.mjs
